    </Boolean>
  </CalDefinition>
  <CalDefinition Description="The APA application is an application that gives you the information about APA provided with the vehicle. The APA calibration is used to Enable/Disable the display of this Application on the HomeScreen and in the App Tray. When this calibration is set to True (Enabled), this HomeScreen Application shall be displayed on the HomeScreen. When this calibration is set to False (Disabled), this HomeScreen Application shall not be displayed on the HomeScreen. " Name="APPLICATION_HOMESCREEN_APA_ENABLED" References="GIS501 SECTION 5.1" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALB,VCU">
