  <CalDefinition Description="RPO Air Quality Sensor to Determine Availability of the Air Quality Application on the HomeScreen and in the App Tray.  As noted in the GIS-551 Air Quality UI, RPO: &quot;USK&quot; is the applicable RPO for Air Quality Sensor to Determine Availability." Name="APPLICATION_HOMESCREEN_AIRQUALITY_ENABLED" References="GIS-501 (Section#s: 3.7.5 and 5.1.1) and GIS-551 (Section #: 5.1.1)" Usage="LOW,MID,HIGH,GEM,GLOBALA,GLOBALB,ENTRY_VCU,VCU">
