      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
      <Version>2</Version>
      <Date>7/1/2016</Date>
      <Description>Updated the description for the APPLICATION_HOMESCREEN_CLIMATE_ENABLED calibration to distinquish between the two different Climate feature calibration: 1.) HvacRadioDisplayEnable (Global A specific calibration) or 2.) Climate Application Available (Global B specific calibration) that should be used as the first/overriding condition for determining if the Climate HomeScreen application icon shall be displayed or not.</Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
    </CalDefChangeRecord>
    <CalDefChangeRecord>
